		<h1 style="color: gold; font-size: 32px">April Audition Camp Registration Confirmation</h1>
		<p style="color: black; font-size:18px; text-align: left;">Dear __firstname,<br>
			<br> Congratulations on taking the first step towards becoming a member of the Arsenal Drum and Bugle Corps by registering for the April Camp!<br>
			<br> At this camp you will be evaluated on your ability to perform as a member of the corps, from playing the show music and exercises to your marching ability and your interactions with staff and other members. We are now working to fill the last few remaining spots in the corps and so we recommend beginning preparation for the camp immediately to help you to have a strong audition.<br>
			<br> Please see the attached General Camp Information document for what to expect at the camp. All audition and materials can be found in the attached Google Drive folder 'Members'. Additionally, within the next 48 hours you should be receiving a PayPal invoice to pay the $50 camp fee. If you do not receive the invoice please message us so that we can resend it. You are also able to pay for camp at check-in by cash or check but note that there will be a $25 convenience fee.<br>
			<br> We look forward to seeing you in April!<br>
			<br>
			<br> Warm Regards,<br> J. Spenser Lotz Executive Director<br> If you have any questions or concerns please email us at contact@arsenalperformingarts.org<br>
